Tag: V00-00-02
2012-03-21 Igor Gaponenko
- the first implementation of the beam-time monitor is complete now.
It brings the database schema, two python applications to separate
EPICS and MySQL contexts (due to an alledged thread management bug in
the Python EPICS code 'pyca'), and a shell script driver ro be run
in a cron job (etc.) for constant monitoring of desired PV values.

